node.text:
Full video is now live over on YouTube.com/AlfieDeyes.
.
Over the past 2 weeks I’ve been working on a Vlogumentary (Mix up between a vlog & documentary). Last night the video went live on my YouTube Channel 👌🏻 Here’s a little snippet for you to get the vibe. Please head over and check out the full 35 minute video and be sure to leave a comment letting me know your thoughts. Creating this was very different to anything I’ve uploaded before and I can’t wait to hear what you think. www.YouTube.com/AlfieDeyes
